= Related Work <related_work>
Prior research on the topic of multiple instance semantic segmentation, covering ways in which the instance imbalance problem posed earlier can be addressed has been conducted and the field has seen attention especially in recent years.
== A Taxonomy of Losses <loss_taxonomy>
A general idea of the current loss landscape in segmentation is proposed in @ma2021lossodyssey. The authors proposed a taxonomy that is valuable in understanding what abstractions can be found in the current thinking and how we can apply these abstractions to enhance problem-specific approaches.
